SUMMARY:🌙 Moon Void — last sextile 🌊Neptune
DESCRIPTION:The Moon drifts into silence on the wings of a Neptune sextile — a gentle dissolving\, an invitation to let the ordinary world recede. This void has a dreamy\, permeable quality. Intuition flows freely here\, but logic tends to slip. Rest in the feeling-space rather than pushing for clarity.\n\nWhat arises when you stop trying to figure things out and simply let yourself feel?
