DESCRIPTION:Mercury enters Capricorn today.\n\nMercury governs thought\, communication\, and how you process information. Capricorn operates through structuring\, achieving\, and building for the long term. For the duration of this transit\, how you think and speak is filtered through Capricorn's capacity for discipline\, ambition\, and the willingness to earn what matters.\n\nIn practical terms: pay attention to what your mind is working on and notice how Capricorn's mode of operation either supports\, challenges\, or transforms it.\n\nWhat are you committed to building — not just trying or wanting\, but actually committed to?
