SUMMARY:🌿 Chiron Direct →
DESCRIPTION:Chiron stations direct today\, resuming forward motion after its retrograde period.\n\nChiron's station direct marks a shift from interior examination to exterior expression — the wound that was being processed internally now begins to manifest in how you engage with the world.\n\nWhat became clear during the Chiron retrograde about the nature of your core wound\, your relationship to vulnerability\, or the places where old pain still operates — that clarity now has somewhere to go. The healing work isn't done (it never fully is)\, but it moves from self-examination into expression\, relationship\, and service.\n\nChiron in Aries (where it's been) going direct is specifically a signal: the wound around the self\, around the right to initiate and exist fully\, is now available to be expressed through action rather than just processed through reflection. The healer-teacher aspect of Chiron — the part that turns wound into gift — is more accessible now.\n\nJoseph Campbell\, writing about mythology and psychology\, noted: 'The cave you fear to enter holds the treasure you seek.' Chiron direct is the moment after you've been in the cave and are carrying something back from it.\n\nWhat understanding about yourself or your wound did you develop in recent months that is now ready to be applied — in your work\, your relationships\, or your self-expression?\n\nAnd: who in your life might benefit from exactly that understanding?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
