SUMMARY:🌕 Full Moon ♋Cancer
DESCRIPTION:Full Moon in Cancer — maximum light\, maximum visibility.\n\nThe Full Moon is the culmination point of the cycle that began at the New Moon roughly two weeks ago. It illuminates what has been growing in the background — not always comfortably. What has been building\, unacknowledged\, unfinished\, or unspoken tends to surface now.\n\nIn Cancer\, Full Moons tend to illuminate: what emotional truth has been living in the background.\n\nWhat has reached its fullness — in a project\, a relationship\, a feeling\, an understanding — and what does that completion ask of you now?
