SUMMARY:🌗 Last Quarter Moon
DESCRIPTION:Last Quarter Moon in Libra — the waning half-moon\, the harvest and release phase.\n\nWe are three-quarters through the lunar cycle. The building is done. The Last Quarter phase is for integrating what the cycle produced\, discarding what didn't work\, and consciously clearing space before the next New Moon opens a fresh chapter.\n\nThis is a better time for finishing than for starting\, for releasing than for acquiring\, for reflecting than for initiating.\n\nWhat from this past cycle are you ready to release — not because it was a failure\, but because it has run its course?
