SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♑Capricorn
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Capricorn — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Capricorn brings its gifts of discipline\, ambition\, and the willingness to earn what matters to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Capricorn's mode.\n\nIn Capricorn\, the focus of this New Moon is: make a concrete commitment to something worth building over time.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,LUNAR
