SUMMARY:🌊 Neptune enters ♈Aries
DESCRIPTION:Neptune enters Aries today for the first time since 1861.\n\nThat transit ran from 1861 to 1875 — the American Civil War\, the abolition of serfdom in Russia\, Darwin's ideas reshaping the human story\, the Paris Commune\, the birth of Impressionism. Not a quiet era. Neptune dissolves old structures\; Aries rebuilds from first principles. The combination tends to produce idealistic upheaval — movements that believe\, with passionate conviction\, they are starting the world over.\n\nNeptune governs what we collectively imagine\, fear\, dream about\, and surrender to. In Pisces (2011-2026) that was: the internet as nervous system\, the blurring of reality and fiction\, mental health as mainstream conversation\, spirituality without institutions. In Aries\, Neptune's fog doesn't disperse — it charges forward. Expect: movements driven more by vision than strategy. Heroes who are partly mythologized. Technology that feels like magic. The line between inspiration and delusion getting very thin.\n\nFor you personally: Neptune in Aries will transit your chart over the next 14 years\, dissolving and reimagining whatever house Aries occupies for you. This is a generational reset of what we believe is possible — which makes it exactly the wrong time to be cynical and exactly the right time to be discerning.\n\nThe question Neptune in Aries asks: What would you fight for if you truly believed it was possible?\n\nAnd the counter-question worth holding alongside it: What are you willing to believe in without demanding proof — and is that faith\, or is it wishful thinking?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,INGRESS
