SUMMARY:⚡ Uranus Direct →
DESCRIPTION:Uranus stations direct today\, resuming forward motion after its retrograde period.\n\nUranus direct is often felt as a release — a resumption of forward movement in the areas where Uranus has been pushing for change. Whatever felt stuck\, constrained\, or internally agitating during the retrograde may now find more external expression.\n\nUranus in Taurus (where it's been since 2018) going direct re-activates the disruption and reinvention happening in the domains of: financial systems\, the body and physical world\, resources and sustainability\, and the structures of material life. The specific area of your chart where Taurus falls is where this forward motion will be felt.\n\nUranus station points (both retrograde and direct) tend to crystallize exactly what needs to change. Direct motion is the invitation to stop analyzing it and start moving with it.\n\nThe physicist Richard Feynman said: 'I would rather have questions that can't be answered '  'than answers that can't be questioned.' Uranus direct is when the questions that accumulated during the retrograde start producing actual experiments.\n\nWhat insight about where you've been constrained — in your material life\, your body\, your relationship to security — is now ready to be acted on rather than just understood?\n\nWhat experiment would you run\, if you were willing to find out what happens?
