SUMMARY:🌟 Jupiter Direct →
DESCRIPTION:Jupiter stations direct today\, resuming forward motion after its retrograde period.\n\nJupiter retrogrades for approximately four months each year. When it turns direct\, the expansion and opportunity that Jupiter represents begins to flow outward again after a period of internal re-assessment.\n\nJupiter retrograde tends to turn the search for meaning\, growth\, and abundance inward — producing re-evaluation of beliefs\, philosophy\, and the stories we tell about what's possible. Optimism that was inflated gets corrected. Genuine faith gets clarified.\n\nJupiter direct resumes the outward expression of that clarified optimism — but now with more honest foundations under it. Growth that happens after Jupiter direct tends to be more sustainable than growth pursued before the retrograde did its review work.\n\nJupiter in Gemini going direct: the expansion of ideas\, communication\, connections\, and learning now resumes with more forward momentum. Projects that stalled — writing\, teaching\, network building\, intellectual development — are well-positioned to regain traction.\n\nWhat belief about what's possible for you was being tested or revised during the past several months?\n\nAnd: now that you have a clearer\, more honest version of that belief\, what becomes available to pursue that wasn't before?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
