SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♓Pisces
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Pisces — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Pisces brings its gifts of compassion\, intuition\, and the permeability that allows real empathy to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Pisces's mode.\n\nIn Pisces\, the focus of this New Moon is: let go of something that no longer needs your effort\, or create from a place of genuine feeling.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
