SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♈Aries
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Aries — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Aries brings its gifts of courage\, directness\, and the willingness to begin to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Aries's mode.\n\nIn Aries\, the focus of this New Moon is: begin something — not plan it\, actually start it.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
