SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♉Taurus
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Taurus — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Taurus brings its gifts of patience\, sensory presence\, and commitment to quality to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Taurus's mode.\n\nIn Taurus\, the focus of this New Moon is: commit to something of real value — not what seems valuable\, but what genuinely is.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
