SUMMARY:💍 Juno Retrograde ℞
DESCRIPTION:Juno stations retrograde today.\n\nJuno governs committed partnership\, contracts\, and the terms of belonging. During its retrograde period\, that domain turns inward — what usually operates through external events and circumstances becomes more available to interior examination and review.\n\nThis is typically a good period for: revisiting decisions related to what you need in deep relationship\, reconsidering anything that was moved past too quickly in Juno's domain\, and doing the slower\, more honest version of whatever how you negotiate equality and loyalty is asking for.\n\nRetrogrades aren't curses — they're pauses with a purpose. What the retrograde period makes available is often exactly what was needed but couldn't be accessed while the forward momentum was in charge.\n\nWhat aspect of committed partnership\, contracts\, and the terms of belonging in your life would benefit from a second\, more careful look?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
