SUMMARY:💕 Venus enters ♌Leo
DESCRIPTION:Venus enters Leo today.\n\nVenus governs what you value\, how you love\, and what draws your attention. Leo operates through expressing\, creating\, and being seen with full authenticity. For the duration of this transit\, what you find beautiful and worth pursuing is filtered through Leo's capacity for generosity\, courage\, and the will to shine.\n\nIn practical terms: pay attention to who and what you are in relationship with and notice how Leo's mode of operation either supports\, challenges\, or transforms it.\n\nWhat would you create or become if you stopped managing how it would be received?
