SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♊Gemini
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Gemini — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Gemini brings its gifts of curiosity\, adaptability\, and the love of ideas to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Gemini's mode.\n\nIn Gemini\, the focus of this New Moon is: ask a question you've been avoiding\, or begin learning something new.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,LUNAR
