SUMMARY:💫 Mercury Retrograde ℞
DESCRIPTION:Mercury stations retrograde today — beginning its apparent backward motion as Earth overtakes Mercury in its orbital path.\n\nMercury is not actually moving backward. From our vantage point on Earth\, it appears to reverse direction three times a year for roughly three weeks each time. This is the same optical effect you experience when passing a slower vehicle on a highway — the other car appears to move backward relative to you\, though it's still moving forward.\n\nMercury governs communication\, contracts\, travel logistics\, technology systems\, and how information moves. During retrograde periods\, these domains tend to require more attention and review — not because magic is at work\, but because retrograde periods correlate with Mercury moving through a region of the sky a second time\, often stirring up what was first passed over too quickly.\n\nThe practical guidance isn't superstition: it's about pace. Retrograde periods are genuinely useful for revision\, review\, re-contacting people\, reconsidering decisions\, and editing work. They're less ideal for launching new ventures that depend on smooth initial communication — not because the planets curse them\, but because the retrograde period itself is better suited to what the 're-' prefix describes.\n\nWhat this retrograde (in Pisces) specifically activates: communication about emotional or spiritual matters\, creative projects\, intuitive insights that need to be re-examined\, and anything where clarity of feeling is more important than clarity of fact.\n\nWhat is asking to be revisited\, reconsidered\, or re-examined in your thinking right now?\n\nWhat did you move past too quickly — a conversation\, a decision\, an understanding — that deserves a second\, more careful look?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
UID:51452a9fcfe8356ad13a41574ee97d1e@quantumelodic.symphony
