DTSTART:20260630T015200Z
DTEND:20260630T025200Z
SUMMARY:🌟 Jupiter enters ♌Leo
DESCRIPTION:Jupiter enters Leo today\, where it will remain for approximately one year.\n\nJupiter expands whatever it touches. In Leo\, it expands the self — creative ambition\, public presence\, the desire to be seen and recognized\, the courage to lead rather than follow. The last Jupiter in Leo transit (2014-2015) produced a noticeable cultural shift toward personal branding\, the rise of YouTube and Instagram culture\, and a general 'everything is content' moment.\n\nThis transit supports: creative output\, performance\, leadership development\, visibility in your field\, romantic boldness\, and anything requiring genuine self-expression. It's a poor time for false modesty. Jupiter in Leo rewards people who actually show their work.\n\nThe risk with Jupiter in Leo: grandiosity. The difference between healthy pride and inflation is whether the accomplishment is real. Jupiter expands both the genuine thing and the ego. The philosopher Aristotle identified 'megalopsychia' — greatness of soul — as a virtue that requires accurately assessing your own worth: not understating it (false humility) and not overstating it (vanity). Jupiter in Leo is a year-long test of that accuracy.\n\nWhere does Jupiter fall in your natal chart? That's where the expansion happens.\n\nWhat creative project\, performance\, or public expression has been waiting for you to believe in it enough to fully commit?\n\nAnd: what would you create if you weren't managing how it would be received?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,INGRESS
