SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♋Cancer
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Cancer — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Cancer brings its gifts of sensitivity\, memory\, and the intelligence of belonging to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Cancer's mode.\n\nIn Cancer\, the focus of this New Moon is: tend to a relationship or create more genuine safety somewhere in your life.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,LUNAR
