SUMMARY:🌿 Chiron Retrograde ℞
DESCRIPTION:Chiron stations retrograde today.\n\nChiron retrogrades every year for roughly five months. Like other outer body retrogrades\, the shift is more qualitative than dramatic — but Chiron's retrograde has a specific quality worth noting.\n\nWhen Chiron is direct\, the wound tends to present externally: through the situations you encounter\, the people who trigger you\, the places where you feel inadequate or out of place. When Chiron is retrograde\, that same process turns inward — the wound becomes more accessible to direct examination rather than available only through external mirrors.\n\nThis is the better time to do actual healing work. Therapy\, somatic work\, honest self-examination\, journaling\, or simply sitting with a wound long enough to understand what it's actually about. The retrograde doesn't make the work easier — it makes the wound more available\, which isn't the same thing.\n\nThe Jungian analyst Robert Johnson wrote: 'The most difficult task a human being can face '  'is to make conscious that which has been unconscious.' Chiron retrograde is the annual window where that task is most directly available.\n\nWhat pain or limitation have you been managing around rather than looking at directly?\n\nWhat would change — in your understanding\, your behavior\, or your relationships — if you were willing to look at it?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
