SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♍Virgo
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Virgo — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Virgo brings its gifts of precision\, practicality\, and care for the details that determine quality to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Virgo's mode.\n\nIn Virgo\, the focus of this New Moon is: address something concrete that you've been managing around.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,LUNAR
