SUMMARY:💍 Juno Direct →
DESCRIPTION:Juno stations direct today\, resuming forward motion after its retrograde period.\n\nJuno governs committed partnership\, contracts\, and the terms of belonging. What was reviewed\, reconsidered\, or processed internally during the retrograde now begins to express itself outward again.\n\nThis is a useful moment to act on whatever clarification the retrograde produced — not to push forward urgently\, but to take the first concrete step on whatever you now understand more clearly about what you need in deep relationship.\n\nWhat did the retrograde period reveal about how you negotiate equality and loyalty that you are now ready to do something about?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
