SUMMARY:🌿 Chiron enters ♈Aries
DESCRIPTION:Chiron enters Aries today.\n\nChiron governs the wound that teaches and the healer who is wounded. Aries operates through initiating\, individuating\, and moving before thinking twice. For the duration of this transit\, old pain that has become — or is becoming — wisdom is filtered through Aries's capacity for courage\, directness\, and the willingness to begin.\n\nIn practical terms: pay attention to how vulnerability becomes strength in practice and notice how Aries's mode of operation either supports\, challenges\, or transforms it.\n\nWhat new beginning has been waiting for you to be bold enough to start it?
