SUMMARY:🌙♌ Moon in Leo ✦
DESCRIPTION:The cosmic stage is set for Leo energy — big-hearted\, expressive\, vital.\n\nThis is expressive\, creative fire — the kind that creates\, celebrates\, and refuses to dim itself for anyone. The invitation today is to let yourself be seen\, play freely\, and give your gifts generously.\n\n🌊 Still in the air: A lingering note from Chiron's move into Aries still colors your gift as someone who has suffered and learned.\n\nHow can you give your gifts more freely\, without holding back?
