SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♎Libra
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Libra — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Libra brings its gifts of harmony\, aesthetic sense\, and the skill of real negotiation to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Libra's mode.\n\nIn Libra\, the focus of this New Moon is: have an honest conversation\, or make a decision you've been balancing indefinitely.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
