SUMMARY:🔮 Pluto Direct →
DESCRIPTION:Pluto stations direct today\, resuming forward motion after approximately five months retrograde.\n\nPluto's station direct is subtle but significant — it marks the shift from interior transformation work to exterior manifestation of that work. The processes of deep change that were operating largely below conscious awareness during the retrograde now begin to express themselves in external circumstances.\n\nPluto in Aquarius (where it's been since 2023) going direct re-activates the long-arc transformation of: collective power structures\, technology's relationship to human freedom\, the definition of community and belonging in a networked world\, and what democracy and collective self-determination actually look like under pressure.\n\nOn a personal level\, Pluto direct marks the moment when the internal transformation work — the shadow integration\, the power renegotiation\, the willingness to release what no longer serves — begins to show up in your external life. Not always comfortably.\n\nThe philosopher and depth psychologist James Hillman wrote: 'We don't see things as they are\; we see them as we are.' Pluto's retrograde work is about changing who you are at a deep level. When Pluto goes direct\, you start seeing different things — because you are\, in some essential way\, different.\n\nWhat changed in your sense of your own power or agency over the past several months — even subtly\, even uncomfortably?\n\nAnd: how does that shift want to express itself in the way you engage with the world now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
