DESCRIPTION:Juno enters Aquarius today.\n\nJuno governs committed partnership\, contracts\, and the terms of belonging. Aquarius operates through innovating\, collectivizing\, and thinking past the individual. For the duration of this transit\, what you need in deep relationship is filtered through Aquarius's capacity for originality\, humanitarian vision\, and the refusal to accept things as they are.\n\nIn practical terms: pay attention to how you negotiate equality and loyalty and notice how Aquarius's mode of operation either supports\, challenges\, or transforms it.\n\nWhat do you have to contribute to something larger than your own life?
