SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♏Scorpio
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Scorpio — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Scorpio brings its gifts of depth\, psychological honesty\, and the courage to see what is real to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Scorpio's mode.\n\nIn Scorpio\, the focus of this New Moon is: acknowledge something true that you've been aware of beneath the surface.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,LUNAR
