SUMMARY:🌾 Ceres Retrograde ℞
DESCRIPTION:Ceres stations retrograde today.\n\nCeres governs nourishment\, cycles of loss and return\, and what sustains life. During its retrograde period\, that domain turns inward — what usually operates through external events and circumstances becomes more available to interior examination and review.\n\nThis is typically a good period for: revisiting decisions related to what feeds you at a deep level\, reconsidering anything that was moved past too quickly in Ceres's domain\, and doing the slower\, more honest version of whatever how you care for yourself and others is asking for.\n\nRetrogrades aren't curses — they're pauses with a purpose. What the retrograde period makes available is often exactly what was needed but couldn't be accessed while the forward momentum was in charge.\n\nWhat aspect of nourishment\, cycles of loss and return\, and what sustains life in your life would benefit from a second\, more careful look?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
