SUMMARY:🌑 New Moon ♐Sagittarius
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Sagittarius — the monthly reset point\, when Sun and Moon occupy the same degree and the lunar cycle begins again from zero.\n\nThe lunation cycle mirrors natural growth patterns: New Moon (seed)\, First Quarter (commitment)\, Full Moon (culmination)\, Last Quarter (harvest and release). Each phase has its own relationship to intention and action. Sagittarius brings its gifts of freedom\, enthusiasm\, and the conviction that life has direction to this fresh start. The new beginning available here has that quality — not a generic reset\, but one flavored specifically by Sagittarius's mode.\n\nIn Sagittarius\, the focus of this New Moon is: orient toward something meaningful — a direction\, not just a destination.\n\nWhat do you genuinely want to call into being in this new cycle — not what you think you should want\, but what actually matters to you right now?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,LUNAR
