SUMMARY:🌊 Neptune Direct →
DESCRIPTION:Neptune stations direct today\, resuming apparent forward motion after five months retrograde.\n\nNeptune's station direct tends to feel like a shift in the quality of imagination — creative\, spiritual\, and intuitive energies that were turned inward begin to flow outward again. What was processed internally during the retrograde now wants expression.\n\nNeptune has been in Aries since January — a placement that hasn't occurred since 1861. This station direct in Aries marks the first time Neptune turns direct in this sign in over 160 years. The quality of vision\, idealism\, and spiritual seeking that Neptune in Aries generates is now\, once again\, pointing outward.\n\nThis is a good moment to revisit creative or spiritual projects that stalled or went underground during the retrograde period. Not to force them forward\, but to open the door and see what wants to move.\n\nThe mystic and poet William Blake wrote: 'The imagination is not a state: it is the human existence itself.' Neptune direct is when that faculty returns to full external availability.\n\nWhat vision or creative impulse\, dormant for the past several months\, is ready to be worked with again?\n\nAnd: what did you learn about yourself during the inward period that you want to bring into how you engage with the world?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
