SUMMARY:🌟 Jupiter Retrograde ℞
DESCRIPTION:Jupiter stations retrograde today.\n\nJupiter governs expansion\, meaning-making\, and the hunger for more. During its retrograde period\, that domain turns inward — what usually operates through external events and circumstances becomes more available to interior examination and review.\n\nThis is typically a good period for: revisiting decisions related to what you are growing into\, reconsidering anything that was moved past too quickly in Jupiter's domain\, and doing the slower\, more honest version of whatever where optimism and opportunity are available is asking for.\n\nRetrogrades aren't curses — they're pauses with a purpose. What the retrograde period makes available is often exactly what was needed but couldn't be accessed while the forward momentum was in charge.\n\nWhat aspect of expansion\, meaning-making\, and the hunger for more in your life would benefit from a second\, more careful look?
CATEGORIES:QUANTUMELODIC,STATION
