SUMMARY:🌓 First Quarter Moon
DESCRIPTION:First Quarter Moon in Pisces — the halfway point between the New Moon and the Full.\n\nThis is the moment of friction and commitment. The intention set at the New Moon now meets resistance — the real world pushes back\, circumstances complicate\, the easy path is no longer available. This friction is the point\, not a problem: it's what develops strength and reveals how seriously you actually meant what you set in motion.\n\nFirst Quarter Moons ask for concrete action — not more planning\, not more considering\, but a decision followed by a step.\n\nWhat one specific action would demonstrate that you are genuinely committed to what you set in motion at the New Moon?
