SUMMARY:🌙♑ Moon in Capricorn ✦
DESCRIPTION:A Capricorn current runs beneath the day\, calling you toward disciplined\, meaningful effort.\n\nThis is purposeful\, legacy-building earth — patient with the long road\, serious about what it is building\, and unwilling to cut corners on what matters. The invitation today is to work steadily toward what matters and let your actions speak for themselves.\n\n🌊 Still in the air: The reverberations of recent cosmic shifts still color what you truly need.\n\nWhat would your most mature\, grounded self do with today?
